sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>5001/TCP HTTP
    participant InferencePod as Inference Service Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation and Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>HTTPS/6443 + User Auth
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>HTTPS/6443 + ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route<br/>HTTPS/6443 + ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Gateway<br/>HTTPS/6443 + ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create VirtualService<br/>HTTPS/6443 + ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PeerAuthentication<br/>HTTPS/6443 + ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthConfig<br/>HTTPS/6443 + ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>HTTPS/6443 + ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>HTTPS/6443 + ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Model Inference Request (KServe Serverless with Mesh)

    User->>Router: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+ Edge
    Router->>Gateway: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/8080 (internal)
    Gateway->>Authorino: Validate Auth<br/>HTTP/5001 (sidecar)
    Authorino-->>Gateway: Auth Result
    Gateway->>InferencePod: Inference Request<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS Client Cert
    InferencePod->>S3: Load Model Artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+ AWS Signature
    S3-->>InferencePod: Model Data
    InferencePod-->>Gateway: Prediction Result
    Gateway-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Controller: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 + ServiceAccount Token
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Controller Metrics

    Prometheus->>InferencePod: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    InferencePod-->>Prometheus: Inference Metrics

    Note over User,S3: Flow 4: Storage Configuration Propagation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create Data Connection Secret<br/>HTTPS/6443 + User Auth
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Secret Event<br/>HTTPS/6443 + ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Aggregate into storage-config<br/>HTTPS/6443 + ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>InferencePod: Mount storage-config Secret<br/>K8s Secret Mount
